{"tid":353502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 美B-1B轟炸機飛越朝鮮半島　做好「今夜開戰」準備","createTime":"2017-08-09T15:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T00:23:51.000Z","uid":53705,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6cdd88ae0f48198352bba5c21c56c1eb4bfbcdcf","tid":353502,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170809002557-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20170809002557-260408&d=t4nFgH9TD0C6R7MlJds7rkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=53db69a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20170809002557-260408</a><br />\n<br />\n美軍一名在關島的B-1B戰略轟炸機飛行員也表示，美、日、韓三軍的訓練與作戰方式都和以往一樣，與盟友舉行愈多的演習讓他們更加爐火純青，也讓他們可以做好「今夜開戰」的準備，美國空軍也在推特上發了一則推文表示，美軍轟炸機從南達科他州抵達關島，展開雙邊演習，並標記了「今晚開戰」<br />\n<br />\n打了打了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d189a3eb1c6b901184aedced5c51c1e76cfa8002","tid":353502,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:45:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70ae8f04304679fc7a065d0ab973d95457dc706b","tid":353502,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:45:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b82970a8a9b1540718046a3955521eb525fd627","tid":353502,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:47:14.000Z","msg":"食屎啦，朱仔成"},{"pid":"383502ae10dc88b236d4f6cce41d49b339b288a7","tid":353502,"uid":98232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:51:28.000Z","msg":"今晚開戰夜唔夜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a29eec862f5e6e884383d98e36b293f5d5e202ba","tid":353502,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T15:51:59.000Z","msg":"<block